    "content": "<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 您好，为适应业务发展需求，将修订《<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif;\">京东开放平台个人/个体合规管理规则</span>》，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年3月19日- </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">2025年3月25日，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\">规则预计于2025年3月26日生效，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> </span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">核心调整点：调整不正当手段获取资源中&ldquo;违规程度一般&rdquo;的违约金范围</span></span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">。</span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">原规则链接：<a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=923540006109319168&amp;btype=12\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=923540006109319168&amp;btype=12</a></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\">\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 475.0pt; border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"0\" width=\"633\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 14.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 239.0pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: red; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"319\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 2\\.0 玲珑'; color: white;\">修订前</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 236.0pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: red; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"315\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 2\\.0 玲珑'; color: white;\">修订后</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 69.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 239.0pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 69.5pt;\" width=\"319\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 2\\.0 玲珑'; color: black;\">23.2.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 2\\.0 玲珑'; color: black;\">违规程度一般：删除违规商品，店铺商品搜索、推荐降权7日，扣除违约金10000元；</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 236.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 69.5pt;\" width=\"315\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 2\\.0 玲珑'; color: black;\">23.2.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 2\\.0 玲珑'; color: black;\">违规程度一般：删除违规商品，店铺商品搜索、推荐降权7日，扣除违约金5000元至10000元；</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>",
